    - m_Type: 1
      Title:
        m_Untranslated: Fix the DebugHitInfo Function Call in RaycastWithinCircle
      Text:
        m_Untranslated: 'Use the following code:

          <code>

          RaycastUtils.DebugHitInfo(collidersNearMe,
          numberOfCollidersNearMe);

          </code>'
